- Kind of a busy time for you guys, huh?
- In fact, I was in New York.

86
00:10:30,775 --> 00:10:33,899
A detail to the UN. I received a phone call
in the middle of the night.

87
00:10:33,900 --> 00:10:39,062
"Find Professor Robert Langdon. A matter of great urgency."

88
00:10:39,473 --> 00:10:42,393
They said to show you this.

89
00:10:52,519 --> 00:10:55,314
