92
00:11:00,954 --> 00:11:04,789
Now, that's common for a symbol like a Yin and Yang
or a swastika but... that's a word.

93
00:11:05,124 --> 00:11:09,968
That Illuminati ambigramatic symbol has
been considered a myth for 400 years.

94
00:11:10,279 --> 00:11:15,381
Supposedly, in the 16th century, some artist created
it as a tribute to Galileo's love of symmetry.

95
00:11:16,020 --> 00:11:19,451
It was only gonna be revealed when the
Illuminati had amassed enough power

96
00:11:19,452 --> 00:11:23,320
to resurface and carry out their final goal.
I wrote a book about it.

97
00:11:24,189 --> 00:11:25,773
Which is why you're here.

98
00:11:25,742 --> 00:11:28,831
- "The Art of the Illuminati" by Robert Langdon.
- Part One.

99
00:11:29,534 --> 00:11:33,300
I haven't been able to finish Part Two because
I'm not allowed access to your archives.

100
00:11:39,105 --> 00:11:41,473
It's remarkable. Similar.

101
00:11:41,567 --> 00:11:45,659
Someone is trying to make you believe the Illuminati
themselves have returned to Rome.

102
00:11:46,027 --> 00:11:47,992
Right after the death of a pope.

103
00:11:51,687 --> 00:11:57,223
Four cardinals were kidnapped from their quarter's inside
the Vatican sometime between 3 and 5 am this morning.

104
00:11:57,629 --> 00:12:02,319
Shortly afterward, that document was
sent to the office of the Swiss Guard

105
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:09,173
along with the threat the Cardinals will be publicly executed
one per hour begining at 8 pm tonight in Rome.

106
00:12:20,119 --> 00:12:21,204
The conclave?

107
00:12:21,218 --> 00:12:25,310
Was to begin today. We have postponed the start
for a few hours with the story of illness.

108
00:12:25,410 --> 00:12:27,378
There are no suspicions... yet.

109
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:29,967
What do you want from me?

110
00:12:30,920 --> 00:12:36,882
These criminals, who sent this ambigram,
meant it as a taunt, a provocation.

111
00:12:37,136 --> 00:12:43,784
But Captain Olivetti think if you can use it to learn their identity,
perhaps we can stop this abomination.

112
00:12:47,968 --> 00:12:49,043
Why me?

113
00:12:50,007 --> 00:12:53,334
Your expertise. Your erudition.

114
00:12:53,342 --> 00:12:57,719
Your recent involvement with certain church, shall we say...

115
00:12:58,186 --> 00:12:59,025
mysteries.

116
00:13:00,153 --> 00:13:04,233
I wasn't under the impression that episode
had endeared me to the Vatican.

117
00:13:04,239 --> 00:13:05,718
Oh, it didn't.

118
00:13:05,850 --> 00:13:09,269
But it did make you, what is the word for...

119
00:13:09,270 --> 00:13:10,525
"formidable"?

120
00:13:11,187 --> 00:13:12,801
Formidable?

121
00:13:13,825 --> 00:13:16,560
A Vatican jet is standing by twenty minutes from here.

122
00:13:16,565 --> 00:13:18,134
Will you come with me?

123
00:13:25,964 --> 00:13:27,130
Professor Langdon.

124
00:13:27,134 --> 00:13:31,246
You've spent your life searching for symbols
like the one you now hold in your hand.

125
00:13:31,682 --> 00:13:35,711
How much longer are we going to pretend
you have not already decided to come?

126
00:13:42,187 --> 00:13:48,677
If the Illuminati have returned and are in Rome,
we will hunt them down and kill them.

127
00:13:49,687 --> 00:13:53,348
The Illuminati did not become violent until the 17th century.

128
00:13:53,349 --> 00:13:54,763
Their name means 'The Enlightened Ones'.

129
00:13:54,864 --> 00:13:57,836
They were physicists, mathematicians, astronomers.

130
00:13:57,842 --> 00:14:02,719
They were concerned with the church's inaccurate teachings
and they were dedicated to scientific truth.

131
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:04,355
But the Vatican didn't like that.

132
00:14:04,356 --> 00:14:08,444
So, the church began to, how did you say it?
Oh. Hunt them down and kill them.

133
00:14:09,553 --> 00:14:11,784
Drove them underground

134
00:14:12,374 --> 00:14:14,767
into a secret society.

135
00:15:02,842 --> 00:15:04,572
- Professor Langdon.
- Yes?

136
00:15:04,673 --> 00:15:06,617
Welcome to Vatican City.

137
00:15:06,961 --> 00:15:10,735
Ernesto Olivetti, Inspector General of the Vatican Police Force.

138
00:15:10,736 --> 00:15:12,677
- My pleasure.
- This way please.

139
00:15:12,799 --> 00:15:15,658
We'll meet in the headquarters of the Swiss Guard.

140
00:15:15,813 --> 00:15:19,514
- I thought you were Swiss Guard.
- No, uh, the Gendarmaria.

141
00:15:19,515 --> 00:15:22,939
We are responsible for everything inside the Vatican walls

142
00:15:23,274 --> 00:15:26,575
with the exception of the security of His Holiness...

143
00:15:26,576 --> 00:15:28,212
- Yeah.
- and the Apostolic Palace.

144
00:15:28,213 --> 00:15:29,814
That is Swiss Guard.

145
00:15:29,849 --> 00:15:33,443
The Roman Carabinieri are here as
well in an advisory capacity.

146
00:15:33,522 --> 00:15:36,432
- So jurisdictionally this is...
- A goddamn nightmare.

147
00:15:43,528 --> 00:15:47,352
- Oh, yes. Pope Pius IX's great castration.
- I beg your pardon?

148
00:15:47,455 --> 00:15:53,066
1857. Pope Pius IX felt the male form would inspire lust.

149
00:15:53,430 --> 00:15:58,130
So, he took a hammer and chisel and
'un-manned' hundreds of these statues.

150
00:15:58,166 --> 00:16:01,166
The plaster fig leaves were added later.

151
00:16:03,095 --> 00:16:06,650
Are you anti-Catholic, Professor Langdon?

152
00:16:07,077 --> 00:16:10,023
No. I'm anti-vandalism.

153
00:16:13,469 --> 00:16:16,266
I urge you to guard your tone here.

154
00:16:16,432 --> 00:16:24,309
The Swiss Guard is a calling, not a profession,
and it encourages a certain civiltry.

155
00:16:25,177 --> 00:16:29,295
Commander Richter, the head of the Guard,
is a deeply spiritual man.

156
00:16:29,301 --> 00:16:31,516
He was close to the late Pope. Understood?

157
00:16:31,616 --> 00:16:36,857
Look, I dont study symbols because I consider them unimportant.
Ceremony, traditions, heavily mark our lives.

158
00:16:37,020 --> 00:16:40,226
- I just hope I can help.
- So do I.

159
00:16:40,981 --> 00:16:43,048
You were my idea.

160
00:16:53,787 --> 00:16:55,862
Wait here. Please.

161
00:16:59,475 --> 00:17:01,603
Commander? Commander Richter?

162
00:17:08,968 --> 00:17:10,828
Doctor Vetra?

163
00:17:12,131 --> 00:17:16,030
I'm Commander Richter, principal of the Swiss Guard.
Thank you for coming.

164
00:17:16,231 --> 00:17:17,415
Hello.

165
00:17:17,675 --> 00:17:20,076
Oh. Professor Langdon.

166
00:17:20,382 --> 00:17:22,932
What a relief. The symbologist is here.

167
00:17:22,933 --> 00:17:24,920
This way, please, Miss Vetra.

168
00:17:26,589 --> 00:17:28,448
The situation has changed.

169
00:17:28,490 --> 00:17:30,850
We received another threat from the kidnapper.

170
00:17:31,450 --> 00:17:34,506
The canister was stolen from my lab around noon yesterday.

171
00:17:34,650 --> 00:17:40,748
The intruder killed my research partner, Silvano Paintivolio
and mutilated him in order to bypass security.

172
00:17:41,399 --> 00:17:43,147
We use retinal scanners.

173
00:17:43,944 --> 00:17:45,839
They cut out his eye.

174
00:17:46,886 --> 00:17:49,411
Is that your stolen canister, Ms. Vetra?

175
00:17:50,311 --> 00:17:53,200
- Where is that camera, number 86?
- It's wireless.

176
00:17:53,223 --> 00:17:55,700
It, too, was stolen. It could be anywhere
inside the Vatican walls.

177
00:17:55,701 --> 00:17:58,996
That canister contains an extremely combustible
substance called antimatter.

178
00:17:58,997 --> 00:18:02,000
We need to locate it immediately.
We evacuate Vatican City.

179
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:04,607
I'm quite familiar with incendiaries, Miss Vetra.

180
00:18:04,608 --> 00:18:09,666
- I've never heard of antimatter being used as such.
- Well, its never been generated in significant quantities before.

181
00:18:09,745 --> 00:18:15,488
It's a way of studying the origins of the universe.
To try to isolate what some people call "the God Particle".

182
00:18:15,489 --> 00:18:19,211
- But there are implications for energy, research...
- "God Particle"?

183
00:18:20,674 --> 00:18:22,603
What you call it isn't important.

184
00:18:22,605 --> 00:18:26,109
It's what gives all matter mass.
The thing without which we could not exist.

185
00:18:26,110 --> 00:18:31,290
- You're talking about the moment of creation.
- Yes, in a way, I am.

186
00:18:31,514 --> 00:18:33,490
The antimatter is suspended there...

187
00:18:33,690 --> 00:18:37,000
in an airtight nano-composite shell with
electromagnets on each end.

188
00:18:37,291 --> 00:18:41,856
But if it were to fall out of suspension, and come into contact
with matter, say with the bottom of the canister,

189
00:18:41,857 --> 00:18:45,203
then, the two opposing forces would
annihilate one another violently.

190
00:18:45,204 --> 00:18:47,543
What might cause it to fall out of suspension?

191
00:18:47,844 --> 00:18:49,237
The battery going dead.

192
00:18:49,862 --> 00:18:51,852
Which it will just before midnight.

193
00:18:51,963 --> 00:18:55,988
- What kind of annihilation? How violent?
- A cataclysmic event.

194
00:18:56,043 --> 00:18:59,744
A blinding explosion equivalent to about 5 kilotons.

195
00:19:00,395 --> 00:19:03,890
Vatican City will be consumed by light.

196
00:19:05,500 --> 00:19:07,916
Those are the exact words the kidnapper used.

197
00:19:08,288 --> 00:19:10,679
<i>We will destroy your four pillars.</i>

198
00:19:12,423 --> 00:19:17,468
<i>We will brand your Preferiti and sacrifice
them on the altars of science.</i>

199
00:19:18,022 --> 00:19:20,960
<i>Then bring your church down upon you.</i>

200
00:19:21,206 --> 00:19:23,921
<i>Vatican City will be consumed by light.</i>

201
00:19:24,433 --> 00:19:28,446
<i>A shining star at the end of the Path of Illumination.</i>

202
00:19:34,392 --> 00:19:38,224
It's the ancient Illuminati threat.
Destruction of Vatican City through light.

203
00:19:39,060 --> 00:19:42,521
Four pillars. There's your kidnapped cardinals.

204
00:19:42,759 --> 00:19:46,692
You didn't tell me they were the Preferiti,
the favorites to be named the next Pope.

205
00:19:49,353 --> 00:19:50,228
Play it again.

206
00:19:57,540 --> 00:19:59,906
<i>We will destroy your four pillars.</i>

207
00:20:02,313 --> 00:20:03,747
<i>We will brand your Preferiti...</i>

208
00:20:03,748 --> 00:20:04,715
Wait, stop it. Stop.

209
00:20:07,111 --> 00:20:08,144
Brand them?

210
00:20:10,835 --> 00:20:13,372
That's another Illuminati legend.

211
00:20:13,392 --> 00:20:17,590
This one says that there are a set of five 'Brands'.

212
00:20:18,586 --> 00:20:19,882
Each one an ambigram.

213
00:20:19,974 --> 00:20:22,409
The first four are the fundamental elements of science:

214
00:20:22,504 --> 00:20:24,443
earth, air, fire and water.

215
00:20:24,662 --> 00:20:26,399
The fifth is a mystery.

216
00:20:29,276 --> 00:20:30,396
Maybe it's this.

217
00:20:31,462 --> 00:20:33,326
You said they'd be killed publicly.

218
00:20:33,775 --> 00:20:37,112
Yes. Revenge. For La Purga.

219
00:20:38,119 --> 00:20:39,329
La Purga?

220
00:20:40,848 --> 00:20:43,310
Geez, you guys don't even read your own history, do you?

221
00:20:44,490 --> 00:20:53,090
1668. The church kidnapped four Illuminati scientists and branded
each one of them on the chest with the symbol of the cross.

222
00:20:53,335 --> 00:20:55,588
To purge them of their sins and they executed them,

223
00:20:56,260 --> 00:20:59,960
threw their bodies out in the street as a
warning to others to stop questioning

224
00:20:59,962 --> 00:21:06,325
church rulings on scientific matters. They radicalized them.
The Purga created a darker, more violent Illuminati.

225
00:21:06,327 --> 00:21:08,826
One bent on... on retribution.

226
00:21:09,592 --> 00:21:12,717
And look how they intend to finally get it. Using anti-matter.

227
00:21:12,785 --> 00:21:17,282
Technology to destroy the church.
Science obliterates religion.

228
00:21:18,425 --> 00:21:19,411
Is there any more?

229
00:21:21,529 --> 00:21:24,054
<i>and sacrifice them on the altars of science.</i>

230
00:21:24,704 --> 00:21:26,934
<i>Then bring your church down upon you.</i>

231
00:21:27,898 --> 00:21:30,588
<i>Vatican City will be consumed by light.</i>

232
00:21:31,137 --> 00:21:35,173
<i>A shining star at the end of the Path of Illumination.</i>

233
00:21:35,273 --> 00:21:36,724
Path of Illumination?

234
00:21:40,580 --> 00:21:42,449
I need access to the Vatican archives.

235
00:21:44,657 --> 00:21:48,862
