No. Both. You're a physicist?

308
00:26:45,025 --> 00:26:48,095
Bioentanglement Physics.
The interconnective life systems?

309
00:26:48,095 --> 00:26:49,096
Okay.

310
00:26:49,683 --> 00:26:52,556
Your project... it was to give towards the energy research?

311
00:26:52,741 --> 00:26:53,724
Eventually, yes.

