316
00:27:09,488 --> 00:27:13,822
Who didn't think the church and science were enemies
but just a different language telling the same story.

317
00:27:13,823 --> 00:27:16,158
Anyone of like minds could find the Church of Illumination.

318
00:27:16,159 --> 00:27:20,181
But he couldn't exactly advertise its location,
so he created a coded path.

319
00:27:22,482 --> 00:27:25,212
Richter has started to turn off the power at various rates.

