00:27:27,837 --> 00:27:31,368
Then some unknown Illuminati master sculpted four statues.

322
00:27:31,818 --> 00:27:34,400
Each one a tribute to one of the fundamental elements:

323
00:27:34,402 --> 00:27:36,292
earth, air, fire, water.

