00:28:47,304 --> 00:28:50,712
And, yet, was ensured to wrought my power in great elective.

339
00:28:50,755 --> 00:28:52,639
The cruelest honor in Christendom.

340
00:28:52,942 --> 00:28:55,903
I have no personal ambitions, Patrick.

