00:32:33,485 --> 00:32:36,470
It must. Now of all times.

368
00:32:36,885 --> 00:32:39,691
May God forgive you for what you have done.

369
00:32:47,340 --> 00:32:49,777
Father, if God has issues,

370
00:32:50,207 --> 00:32:52,267
they won't be with what I've done.

371
00:32:53,433 --> 00:32:55,960
They will be with what I'm about to do.

372
00:33:16,928 --> 00:33:22,170
It was confiscated from the Netherlands
by the Vatican just after Galileo died.

373
00:33:22,205 --> 00:33:27,200
I've been petitioning to see it for about ten years.
Ever since I realized what was in it.

374
00:33:27,201 --> 00:33:30,563
- What makes you so sure that this thing is there?
- The number 503.

375
00:33:30,839 --> 00:33:34,920
I kept seeing it, over and over again. In Illuminati letters.

376
00:33:34,921 --> 00:33:38,424
Scribbled in the margins. Sometimes just signed '503'.

