00:34:14,120 --> 00:34:17,179
And sold dozens of copies at the Harvard bookstore.

386
00:34:17,914 --> 00:34:19,308
Il Diagramma Veritatis.

387
00:34:20,446 --> 00:34:21,552
Diagram of Truth.

