00:37:22,138 --> 00:37:24,863
- Raphael? The sculptor?
- Yeah. Santi was his last name.

435
00:37:25,160 --> 00:37:28,834
- So, the path starts at Raphael's tomb?
- Raphael's buried at the Pantheon.

436
00:37:29,384 --> 00:37:32,393
- Isn't the Pantheon a church?
- The oldest Catholic church in Rome.

437
00:37:51,818 --> 00:37:54,298
I just pulled a dozen of my best men for this.

438
00:37:55,206 --> 00:37:56,136
You better be right.

