708
01:04:40,916 --> 01:04:45,104
No. The walls are lead lined.
There's no signal.

709
01:07:59,535 --> 01:08:00,540
This way.

710
01:08:08,946 --> 01:08:12,626
If the Holy Father was murdered,
the implications are profound.

711
01:08:13,345 --> 01:08:15,254
Vatican security is impenetrable.

712
01:08:15,630 --> 01:08:18,103
No one from the outside could've got anywhere near him.

713
01:08:18,700 --> 01:08:22,392
- It was someone on the inside.
- We can trust no one.

714
01:08:24,272 --> 01:08:27,318
On my screen, no response in zone 7.

715
01:08:28,157 --> 01:08:31,339
We rechon that the battery will soon be empty

716
01:08:32,158 --> 01:08:34,221
and the device will explode shortly before midnight.

717
01:08:56,251 --> 01:08:57,523
Holy Father...

718
01:08:58,663 --> 01:09:02,009
when I was young, you've told me the
voice in my heart was God's voice.

719
01:09:02,744 --> 01:09:05,467
You said I should follow it no matter how painful.

720
01:09:05,774 --> 01:09:06,834
Forgive me.

721
01:09:07,844 --> 01:09:10,369
Please, give me strength.

722
01:09:12,054 --> 01:09:16,065
What I do, I do in the name of everything you believed.

723
01:10:06,752 --> 01:10:08,287
God help us.

724
01:10:21,154 --> 01:10:23,321
Santa Maria della Vittoria.
Do you know it?

725
01:10:24,094 --> 01:10:26,207
- Yes, I do.
- It's the next church.

726
01:10:42,567 --> 01:10:44,521
I think someone just tried to kill me.

727
01:10:44,629 --> 01:10:46,317
Professor, I promise you, we had no idea.

728
01:10:46,318 --> 01:10:47,552
- He knows I'm here?
- Yes.

729
01:10:47,553 --> 01:10:49,437
You heard me ask permission.
You gave me an escort.

730
01:10:49,438 --> 01:10:53,604
Yes, but we had no idea that portions of our white zones
were crosswired with that building.

731
01:10:55,120 --> 01:10:56,741
Commander Richter was extending the search.

732
01:10:56,743 --> 01:10:59,888
If he had known the archives were on that grid,
he never would have killed the power.

733
01:11:01,127 --> 01:11:03,087
But there is the other possibility.

734
01:11:03,571 --> 01:11:06,172
Is it conceivable the Illuminati...

735
01:11:07,019 --> 01:11:09,203
have infiltrated the Swiss Guard?

736
01:11:12,160 --> 01:11:13,454
Perhaps.

737
01:11:23,492 --> 01:11:25,239
The journals. Where are they?

738
01:11:27,842 --> 01:11:29,867
Who took the journals from this desk?

739
01:11:39,770 --> 01:11:42,795
Signore, this is unacceptable.

740
01:11:43,092 --> 01:11:46,372
For a Camerlengo to enter the chapel
once conclave has begun.

741
01:11:46,379 --> 01:11:47,656
Forgive me.

742
01:11:47,657 --> 01:11:49,479
There's been a development.

743
01:11:59,637 --> 01:12:02,673
His Holiness Celestine was murdered!

744
01:12:02,674 --> 01:12:05,720
- Is it so inconceivable that it will happen again?
- Signori.

745
01:12:06,290 --> 01:12:09,553
Signori, please, a moment.
Please. Signori.

746
01:12:12,153 --> 01:12:14,467
Our church is at war.

747
01:12:15,540 --> 01:12:18,786
We are under attack from an old enemy.

748
01:12:19,145 --> 01:12:20,970
The Illuminati.

749
01:12:21,466 --> 01:12:23,386
They have struck us from within.

750
01:12:23,690 --> 01:12:26,086
Murdering our Holy Father!

751
01:12:26,221 --> 01:12:30,748
And threatening us all with destruction
at the hands of their new God 'Science'.

752
01:12:30,862 --> 01:12:34,109
They call it retribution.
They think it justified...

753
01:12:34,144 --> 01:12:38,291
because of the Church's attacks on men of
science in the distant past and it's true.

754
01:12:38,999 --> 01:12:44,064
Since the days of Galileo, this church has tried to
slow the relentless march of progress.

755
01:12:44,380 --> 01:12:46,833
Sometimes with misguided means.

756
01:12:47,942 --> 01:12:50,134
But science and religion are not enemies.

757
01:12:51,550 --> 01:12:56,220
There are simply some things that science
is just too young to understand.

758
01:12:56,650 --> 01:12:58,396
So the Church pleads, "Stop."

759
01:12:58,930 --> 01:13:00,191
"Slow down."

760
01:13:00,273 --> 01:13:01,721
"Think. Wait."

761
01:13:01,900 --> 01:13:04,265
And, for this, they call us backwards.

762
01:13:04,884 --> 01:13:06,844
But who is more ignorant?

763
01:13:07,074 --> 01:13:09,178
The man who cannot define lightning...

764
01:13:09,341 --> 01:13:12,450
or the man who does not respect its natural awesome power?

765
01:13:13,539 --> 01:13:15,685
The battle is well under way, signori.

766
01:13:16,719 --> 01:13:18,350
We must defend ourselves.

767
01:13:18,658 --> 01:13:21,127
But, what if this time, we fight their stealth with openness?

768
01:13:21,302 --> 01:13:23,989
Combat their wicked scheme with simple truth.

769
01:13:24,282 --> 01:13:27,133
And end this brutish battle once and for all.

770
01:13:27,328 --> 01:13:30,142
If the outside world could see this church as I do,

771
01:13:30,346 --> 01:13:32,241
looking beyond the ritual of these walls,

772
01:13:32,438 --> 01:13:35,172
they would see a modern miracle.

773
01:13:35,982 --> 01:13:38,753
A brotherhood of imperfect, simple souls...

774
01:13:38,996 --> 01:13:44,250
who want nothing more than to be voices of compassion
in a world spinning out of control.

775
01:13:46,149 --> 01:13:48,476
Signori, I ask..

776
01:13:50,544 --> 01:13:51,440
I pray...

777
01:13:52,679 --> 01:13:54,961
that you break this conclave.

778
01:13:55,473 --> 01:13:56,829
Open the doors,

779
01:13:57,979 --> 01:14:02,360
evacuate St. Peter's Square and tell the world the truth.

780
01:14:37,332 --> 01:14:38,936
Get him down.

781
01:14:50,617 --> 01:14:52,650
There. There, that chain. On that pulley.

782
01:14:52,677 --> 01:14:55,008
This bench. Get this pew off here and make it a ladder.

783
01:16:16,829 --> 01:16:18,129
Vatican Police.

784
01:17:20,764 --> 01:17:22,895
My son...

785
01:17:23,430 --> 01:17:26,371
God answers all prayers, but...

786
01:17:27,173 --> 01:17:29,564
sometimes His answer is no.

787
01:17:31,037 --> 01:17:33,625
The College will not break conclave.

788
01:17:34,862 --> 01:17:36,738
May I suggest...

789
01:17:37,133 --> 01:17:42,151
you direct your energies to helping the Swiss Guard
find this explosive device.

790
01:17:42,656 --> 01:17:43,828
If it exists.

791
01:17:45,508 --> 01:17:47,733
And leave Church leadership...

792
01:17:49,459 --> 01:17:51,282
to its leaders.

793
01:18:03,362 --> 01:18:04,692
Eminence.

794
01:18:07,154 --> 01:18:09,131
There is a growing fear

795
01:18:09,723 --> 01:18:11,980
that without the four Preferiti

796
01:18:11,985 --> 01:18:15,207
it defers much authority for any candidate.

797
01:18:15,208 --> 01:18:16,864
It will not be possible,

798
01:18:17,179 --> 01:18:19,450
- unless...
- Speak plainly.

799
01:18:20,818 --> 01:18:24,449
It is the recommendation of many
that you asked to be removed...

800
01:18:24,455 --> 01:18:26,697
from your post as Great Elector.

801
01:18:27,172 --> 01:18:33,384
Thereby making yourself eligible
to wear the Ring of the Fisherman.

802
01:18:34,692 --> 01:18:37,952
Well, if it is God's will.

803
01:18:45,827 --> 01:18:47,525
May His will be done.

804
01:19:00,822 --> 01:19:03,683
Here! I hear someone.

805
01:19:05,040 --> 01:19:06,455
Remove the lid.

806
01:19:09,111 --> 01:19:09,965
Come on. Come on.

807
01:19:14,428 --> 01:19:15,919
Signore, are you okay?

808
01:19:24,423 --> 01:19:26,146
I know he is there.

809
01:19:26,258 --> 01:19:29,201
Madam, it is necessary that you remain quiet.

810
01:19:29,317 --> 01:19:33,691
Don't tell me that I should remain calm.
I want to know what he will do.

811
01:19:37,640 --> 01:19:39,389
Commander, here's Ms. Vetra.

812
01:19:40,867 --> 01:19:43,412
Those journals are private property.
I demand that you return them to me.

813
01:19:43,414 --> 01:19:46,551
They're material evidence in a Vatican investigation.

814
01:19:49,452 --> 01:19:50,400
I am an Italian citizen.

815
01:19:50,401 --> 01:19:56,400
- My rights do not end just because I crossed the other side.
- This is not Italy. It's not even Rome. It's the Vatican.

816
01:19:56,519 --> 01:19:58,055
A country with its own laws.

817
01:19:58,059 --> 01:20:01,502
And when those journals passed the border,
they became my property.

818
01:20:01,507 --> 01:20:03,231
I will give them back to you

819
01:20:03,857 --> 01:20:06,688
when I've decided they contain nothing
of value to the investigation.

820
01:20:06,891 --> 01:20:09,027
Do you have something to hide, Commandante Richter?

821
01:20:12,352 --> 01:20:13,890
Do you, Dr. Vetra?

822
01:20:35,516 --> 01:20:37,870
If it were up to me, it wouldn't be this way.

823
01:20:39,660 --> 01:20:42,074
It's a sin to kill with pain.

824
01:20:43,324 --> 01:20:45,474
It's a sin to kill without reason, Father.

825
01:20:51,763 --> 01:20:53,125
They made me a sinner.

826
01:21:12,877 --> 01:21:14,549
Saint Theresa on fire.

827
01:21:18,044 --> 01:21:19,225
Professor Langdon?

828
01:21:20,543 --> 01:21:22,695
- What direction is that?
- West, I think.

829
01:21:22,790 --> 01:21:24,705
"Across Rome the mystic elements unfold."

830
01:21:26,848 --> 01:21:31,629
Piazza Barba Rini is here.
Saint Theresa is here.

831
01:21:32,560 --> 01:21:34,661
Where is the Santa Maria del Popolo, the first altar of science?

832
01:21:34,769 --> 01:21:36,085
- Santa Maria del Popolo?
- Yes.

833
01:21:38,502 --> 01:21:39,464
Thank you.

834
01:21:40,339 --> 01:21:41,935
St. Peter's is here.

835
01:21:42,601 --> 01:21:44,274
We are here.

836
01:21:46,243 --> 01:21:47,948
A church with water.

837
01:21:50,000 --> 01:21:51,401
Wait. Wait, wait.

838
01:21:51,817 --> 01:21:53,195
Across Rome.

839
01:21:55,559 --> 01:21:57,338
The poem must mean it's literally across Rome.

840
01:21:57,465 --> 01:21:58,414
Professor Langdon.

841
01:21:58,414 --> 01:22:01,177
Commander Richter has ordered me to escort
you to the Vatican immediately.

842
01:22:01,409 --> 01:22:05,969
Piazza Navona. Earth. Air. Fire. Water.

843
01:22:06,603 --> 01:22:08,142
"A-Cross" Rome.

844
01:22:08,695 --> 01:22:10,252
Bernini's Four Rivers.

845
01:22:11,891 --> 01:22:14,841
Professor Langdon, the Vatican insists that
I have to take you back immediately.

846
01:22:15,058 --> 01:22:17,301
The Vatican is about to see its fourth cardinal murdered tonight.

847
01:22:17,505 --> 01:22:18,611
Now, look.

848
01:22:19,500 --> 01:22:22,239
You can do as they say and force me back to the Vatican,

849
01:22:22,752 --> 01:22:24,433
where we can all mourn his death together.

850
01:22:24,434 --> 01:22:27,097
Or you can show me how real cops act

851
01:22:27,527 --> 01:22:31,220
and take me to Piazza Navona,
where we still might be able to stop it.

852
01:22:34,336 --> 01:22:36,293
Oh. By all means, let's talk it over.

853
01:22:37,520 --> 01:22:39,225
In fourteen minutes, he's going to be dead.

854
01:22:45,139 --> 01:22:46,578
Okay. This way, Professor.

855
01:22:55,288 --> 01:22:56,525
Yes, Padre?

856
01:22:57,035 --> 01:22:59,718
At 11:15, if the church is still in peril,

857
01:23:01,056 --> 01:23:02,957
give the order to evacuate the cardinals.

858
01:23:04,270 --> 01:23:05,791
But with dignity.

859
01:23:06,280 --> 01:23:09,407
Let them walk out into St. Peter's Square
with their heads held high.

860
01:23:10,171 --> 01:23:14,544
We don't want the last image of this church to be of
frightened old men sneaking out the back door.

861
01:23:31,204 --> 01:23:32,634
"Where the angels guide thee..."

862
01:23:38,510 --> 01:23:40,852
There it is. There it is.

863
01:23:40,912 --> 01:23:42,880
Professor, I know this fountain.
There is no angel.

864
01:23:43,086 --> 01:23:45,846
The dove. The angel of peace.

865
01:23:45,927 --> 01:23:47,520
And it's looking in what direction?

866
01:23:48,077 --> 01:23:49,519
Uh... east, I think.

867
01:24:00,908 --> 01:24:03,613
Professor, just wait here. Stay put.

868
01:24:39,400 --> 01:24:41,339
Good evening. Can you help me?

869
01:24:41,946 --> 01:24:44,166
I need a doctor.

870
01:24:59,756 --> 01:25:01,034
Come here.

871
01:25:04,228 --> 01:25:05,225
Calm down. Don't shoot.

872
01:25:05,726 --> 01:25:06,826
Don't shoot.

873
01:25:42,464 --> 01:25:44,124
Hey!

874
01:25:57,935 --> 01:26:00,584
Help! Somebody help!

875
01:26:37,975 --> 01:26:39,181
Help! Somebody!

876
01:27:50,738 --> 01:27:51,723
Cardinal Baja.

877
01:27:52,721 --> 01:27:53,652
Cardinal Baja.

878
01:27:54,418 --> 01:27:55,444
Si?

879
01:27:55,726 --> 01:27:57,472
Where was he hiding you?

880
01:27:58,170 --> 01:28:00,339
The Church of Illumination.
Where is it?

881
01:28:01,284 --> 01:28:03,742
Castel Sant'Angelo.

882
01:28:05,394 --> 01:28:07,095
Castle of the Angel.

883
01:28:28,543 --> 01:28:30,718
Sir, there's news about Cardinal Baja.

884
01:28:31,955 --> 01:28:35,316
The cardinal told Langdon he was being
held in Castel Sant'Angelo.

885
01:28:35,594 --> 01:28:37,844
If Langdon's right, that's where the bomb is.

886
01:28:38,421 --> 01:28:41,072
- Send everyone we can spare.
- And you?

887
01:28:41,422 --> 01:28:42,476
I'm staying here.

888
01:28:55,847 --> 01:28:57,001
Vittoria.

889
01:28:58,265 --> 01:28:59,890
- You're all right?
- I'm all right, yes. What about you?

890
01:28:59,892 --> 01:29:01,568
I just heard about Olivetti on the radio.

891
01:29:01,569 --> 01:29:02,641
I'm all right. I'm okay.

892
01:29:08,838 --> 01:29:12,077
Robert, we can't trust Richter.
He took Silvano's journals.

893
01:29:12,136 --> 01:29:14,209
There must be something in there he doesn't want us to see.

894
01:29:14,830 --> 01:29:16,348
The head of the Swiss Guard.

895
01:29:18,463 --> 01:29:22,888
From the Castel Sant'Angelo. It's close enough so the wireless
signal from that camera could still reach the Vatican.

896
01:29:24,466 --> 01:29:26,854
The Church of Illumination is somewhere here

897
01:29:27,586 --> 01:29:29,402
and your canister is inside it.

898
01:29:49,520 --> 01:29:50,605
Come with me.

899
01:29:54,649 --> 01:29:57,820
For 400 years, the Illuminati met right under the Church's nose.

900
01:29:57,925 --> 01:30:00,981
The Vatican used this as a hideout and
as a prison for their enemies.

901
01:30:01,602 --> 01:30:05,551
If the explosion happens here,
would the blast radius take out the Vatican?

902
01:30:06,223 --> 01:30:08,015
And part of Rome along with it.

903
01:30:26,190 --> 01:30:27,598
They're pointing to it. The angels.

904
01:30:28,178 --> 01:30:29,317
The container must be down there.
Come on!

905
01:31:16,133 --> 01:31:18,435
- Where are they going?
- Back to search the other castle.

906
01:31:18,436 --> 01:31:20,781
No, no. It has to be here!

907
01:31:25,485 --> 01:31:26,985
Robert, it's a dead end.

908
01:31:27,590 --> 01:31:28,622
No, it's not.

909
01:31:29,550 --> 01:31:31,146
See if you can find a flashlight.

910
01:31:48,187 --> 01:31:50,142
All of these stones are rectangular granite.

911
01:31:50,724 --> 01:31:52,594
Except right here. What is this?

912
01:31:57,330 --> 01:31:58,462
It's a pentagram.

913
01:31:58,823 --> 01:31:59,860
An eye...

914
01:32:00,611 --> 01:32:01,842
that leads to...

915
01:32:02,146 --> 01:32:03,002
Nowhere.

916
01:32:12,369 --> 01:32:13,369
Robert?

917
01:32:15,506 --> 01:32:18,174
These walls overlap and there's a passageway in here.

918
01:32:18,175 --> 01:32:19,723
Here. Let me have the flashlight.

919
01:32:42,407 --> 01:32:45,249
It's a passageway that leads to the Vatican.

920
01:32:45,550 --> 01:32:47,748
An ancient escape route.

921
01:32:49,731 --> 01:32:51,454
Oh, God.

922
01:32:53,563 --> 01:32:54,451
Here.

923
01:32:57,031 --> 01:32:58,251
Look.

924
01:33:30,151 --> 01:33:31,566
Get on the radio.

925
01:33:31,567 --> 01:33:34,169
Get the word out.
Conclave remains sealed.

926
01:33:34,170 --> 01:33:37,888
- But the Camerlengo gave the order for evacuation at...
- I'm counter-manning it.

927
01:33:43,802 --> 01:33:45,791
This is it. This is their church.

928
01:33:48,318 --> 01:33:50,799
The canister should be lit by artificial light.

929
01:34:13,843 --> 01:34:15,016
It's not here, Robert.

930
01:34:15,066 --> 01:34:17,361
"The shining star at the end of the path."
It has to be.

931
01:34:17,769 --> 01:34:19,520
It's not here.

932
01:34:19,702 --> 01:34:21,857
- What's the poem say?
- Nothing.

933
01:34:21,908 --> 01:34:27,011
Nothing. It's all over. There was just four lines,
each one describing...

934
01:34:35,947 --> 01:34:37,695
There's a fifth brand.

935
01:34:37,745 --> 01:34:39,776
It's not an ambigram.
It's just two crossed keys.

936
01:34:39,977 --> 01:34:42,621
- The symbol for the Vatican.
- No.

937
01:34:43,428 --> 01:34:46,113
No, the papacy.
They intend to kill him.

938
01:34:46,448 --> 01:34:48,000
Before they destroy the Vatican,

939
01:34:48,700 --> 01:34:51,504
- they're going to brand and kill the pope himself.
- There is no pope.

940
01:34:51,773 --> 01:34:53,629
"Tempo Sede Vacante."

941
01:34:53,764 --> 01:34:55,865
The Camerlengo.

942
01:34:57,105 --> 01:34:59,764
- We have to warn him.
- Take a step back, please.

943
01:35:01,091 --> 01:35:03,513
Take your cell phone from your pocket.

944
01:35:06,663 --> 01:35:08,404
Throw it in the fire.

945
01:35:18,700 --> 01:35:20,025
Murderer.

946
01:35:20,360 --> 01:35:22,584
You know, when they call me,

947
01:35:23,000 --> 01:35:24,342
and they all call me,

948
01:35:25,077 --> 01:35:29,940
it is so important to them that I know that
what they ask is the Lord's will.

949
01:35:30,580 --> 01:35:33,020
Or Allah's. Or Yahweh's.

950
01:35:34,600 --> 01:35:36,459
And I suppose they're right.

951
01:35:40,303 --> 01:35:44,344
Because if he was not vengeful, I would not exist, now, would I?

952
01:35:44,677 --> 01:35:47,299
I've had several chances to eliminate you tonight.

953
01:35:47,606 --> 01:35:51,111
You're still alive because you have no weapon.
And they didn't ask me to kill you.

954
01:35:51,179 --> 01:35:54,328
But if you pursue me, it is another matter.

955
01:36:01,063 --> 01:36:02,278
Be careful.

956
01:36:02,846 --> 01:36:04,725
These are men of God.

957
01:36:16,887 --> 01:36:18,084
The Camerlengo.

958
01:36:26,706 --> 01:36:28,529
Have you come to make me a martyr?

959
01:36:36,448 --> 01:36:37,462
Here. Here.

960
01:38:01,433 --> 01:38:03,056
- I need to see the Camerlengo.
- He is not available.

961
01:38:03,158 --> 01:38:05,690
- I demand to see the Camerlengo!
- He is not available.

962
01:38:07,377 --> 01:38:08,759
We'll see about that.

963
01:38:17,907 --> 01:38:20,619
Oh. It's a chiusa chiave.
It's a one way portal.

964
01:38:20,959 --> 01:38:22,781
The only entrance is on the other side.

965
01:38:23,034 --> 01:38:25,451
No. Hey! Help!

966
01:38:33,530 --> 01:38:35,929
This is Robert Langdon and Dr. Vetra. Open the door.

967
01:38:49,006 --> 01:38:50,670
The Camerlengo is in danger.

968
01:39:04,058 --> 01:39:06,414
He's the one. He's got a gun.

969
01:39:09,882 --> 01:39:11,804
- Illuminatus!
- You bastard.

970
01:39:11,805 --> 01:39:13,173
Illuminatus!

971
01:39:14,074 --> 01:39:14,906
You bastard!

972
01:39:22,644 --> 01:39:23,709
Padre?

973
01:39:23,684 --> 01:39:27,837
Order the evacuation.
We only have nineteen minutes.

974
01:39:30,978 --> 01:39:32,608
Here. He's...

975
01:39:32,693 --> 01:39:34,994
And get the helicopter for the older cardinals, right?

976
01:39:34,995 --> 01:39:35,695
Yes, sir.

977
01:39:49,000 --> 01:39:49,926
Robert?

978
01:39:50,289 --> 01:39:52,848
The brand, the symbol.
Could it have another meaning?

979
01:39:59,184 --> 01:40:02,382
Crossed keys, but those were upside down.

980
01:40:02,417 --> 01:40:03,982
St. Peter.

981
01:40:04,700 --> 01:40:06,671
The first pope...

982
01:40:07,774 --> 01:40:10,643
- was crucified upside down.
- On Vatican Hill.

983
01:40:10,649 --> 01:40:13,512
- A few hundred feet below us.
- Necropolis. City of the dead.

984
01:40:13,514 --> 01:40:16,058
"Upon this rock, I will build my church."

985
01:40:16,059 --> 01:40:18,688
"Or bring it down upon itself."

986
01:40:19,464 --> 01:40:22,682
The bomb. It's in St. Peter's tomb.

987
01:40:36,910 --> 01:40:38,435
The grid is still cycling.

988
01:40:38,436 --> 01:40:40,541
The power to this section must be down.

989
01:41:26,008 --> 01:41:29,012
It must be here. It must be.

990
01:41:39,706 --> 01:41:40,977
Don't touch it.

991
01:41:42,482 --> 01:41:44,032
We have seven minutes.

992
01:41:49,642 --> 01:41:52,139
Robert, hold this.

993
01:42:31,143 --> 01:42:33,093
It's cold down here, isn't it?

994
01:42:33,697 --> 01:42:35,256
What's wrong?

995
01:42:35,143 --> 01:42:37,879
Cold decreases battery life.

996
01:42:39,777 --> 01:42:43,202
- We may have less than five minutes.
- So?

997
01:42:43,300 --> 01:42:46,134
If I pull the power with less than five minutes...

998
01:42:46,139 --> 01:42:49,070
the residual charge won't hold suspension.

999
01:42:50,320 --> 01:42:54,019
We should leave it here and get clear if we can.
At least down here the damage...

1000
01:42:54,020 --> 01:42:54,602
No!

1001
01:42:55,565 --> 01:42:57,532
- No. Wait!
- Father!

1002
01:42:59,810 --> 01:43:05,306
We are live here at St. Peter's Square where, despite
a bomb threat, and an orderly evacuation,

1003
01:43:05,307 --> 01:43:07,774
the crowd is actually growing in size.

1004
01:43:07,979 --> 01:43:12,777
As we await an official announcement from the Vatican
spokesman as to the exact nature of the threat

1005
01:43:12,778 --> 01:43:15,944
and whether or not they are treating it as a credible danger...

1006
01:43:24,198 --> 01:43:25,202
This way!

1007
01:43:54,251 --> 01:43:55,383
He's got a bomb with him.

1008
01:43:56,621 --> 01:43:57,682
A bomb?

1009
01:44:02,947 --> 01:44:05,604
Roberto, this is an emergency.
I'll take her up alone.

1010
01:44:10,219 --> 01:44:12,269
He's got clearance.

1011
01:44:36,214 --> 01:44:38,376
Oh, my God.

1012
01:46:34,912 --> 01:46:36,553
Get down!

1013
01:49:21,928 --> 01:49:23,152
Cardinal Strauss?

1014
01:49:23,952 --> 01:49:27,527
It was the Camerlengo.
He has saved us all.

1015
01:49:28,220 --> 01:49:32,048
He has saved the Church and he's still alive.

1016
01:49:32,606 --> 01:49:34,617
Praise God. Praise God.

1017
01:49:39,889 --> 01:49:41,130
He is alive.

1018
01:49:41,442 --> 01:49:44,378
He sacrificed himself for all of us.

1019
01:50:11,566 --> 01:50:14,341
You know the worst thing we thought would happen

1020
01:50:15,517 --> 01:50:18,831
was that our work would fall into the
hands of the energy companies.

1021
01:50:21,573 --> 01:50:23,500
We thought we could change the world.

1022
01:50:24,178 --> 01:50:27,964
- So naive.
- No, not naive.

1023
01:50:29,274 --> 01:50:30,545
Innocent, maybe.

1024
01:50:31,114 --> 01:50:33,452
But it's not a crime.

1025
01:50:34,702 --> 01:50:36,090
I'm not so sure.

1026
01:50:38,348 --> 01:50:40,006
Go back to work.

1027
01:50:41,501 --> 01:50:43,185
Change the world.

1028
01:51:02,479 --> 01:51:08,382
A gift, uh, you understand?
Let's say for Catholics everywhere.

1029
01:51:08,383 --> 01:51:11,255
The Carmelengo's age shouldn't influence the decision.

1030
01:51:11,434 --> 01:51:17,350
Signori, you are no doubt aware that by Holy Law
the man is inelligible for election to the papacy.

1031
01:51:17,340 --> 01:51:19,327
He's not a cardinal.
He's a priest.

1032
01:51:19,328 --> 01:51:20,597
He's of insufficient age.

1033
01:51:20,807 --> 01:51:23,678
Or maybe there's a way we could consider the possibility.

1034
01:51:24,171 --> 01:51:28,888
I am sorry. The protocols of conclave
are not subject to modification.

1035
01:51:29,008 --> 01:51:30,826
I will not call a ballot on this matter.

1036
01:51:31,032 --> 01:51:33,608
But, signore, you would not hold a ballot.

1037
01:51:33,811 --> 01:51:37,184
Surely, you remember?
You gave up your post as Great Elector.

1038
01:51:38,030 --> 01:51:40,064
They are singing at St. Peter's Square.

1039
01:51:40,152 --> 01:51:42,888
Now, what happened here tonight transcends our laws.

1040
01:51:43,008 --> 01:51:48,888
Has it? Is it God's will that we give ourselves over to frenzy?
Discard the rules of the Church?

1041
01:51:48,890 --> 01:51:52,019
Perhaps we need not discard them.

1042
01:51:52,345 --> 01:51:57,747
Signori, I am thinking now of Romano
Pontifici Eligendo numero 60...

1043
01:51:57,887 --> 01:52:01,081
- Acclamation by Adoration.
- Exactly, signore. Exactly. Yes.

1044
01:52:01,150 --> 01:52:04,144
If the Holy Spirit speaks through us,

1045
01:52:04,269 --> 01:52:09,072
- and we call a man's name out loud...
- That is election by adoration.

1046
01:52:09,073 --> 01:52:11,175
- Yes.
- He's God's choice.

1047
01:52:11,176 --> 01:52:16,840
Yes. And the candidate need only be an
ordained member of the clergy,

1048
01:52:16,841 --> 01:52:21,666
present in the Sistine Chapel at the moment of his election.

1049
01:52:53,253 --> 01:52:55,375
- Signor Camerlengo?
- Yes?

1050
01:52:55,776 --> 01:52:58,857
The cardinals ask you to join them
in conclave as soon as possible.

1051
01:52:59,965 --> 01:53:02,534
- Me?
- Yes, Padre.

1052
01:53:25,125 --> 01:53:25,947
What are you doing?

1053
01:53:26,397 --> 01:53:28,842
Silvano's journals. I want them back.

1054
01:53:52,772 --> 01:53:54,045
Richter said...

1055
01:53:55,866 --> 01:53:59,790
His Holiness suffered from seizures and steps were taken...

1056
01:54:01,121 --> 01:54:02,319
for safety.

1057
01:54:07,000 --> 01:54:09,269
He made sure he was watched, he said.

1058
01:54:11,352 --> 01:54:13,895
What if he were trying to give me this key?

1059
01:54:15,559 --> 01:54:17,026
That's the Papal office.

1060
01:54:17,960 --> 01:54:22,432
If the Pope was worried about seizures, he must've had
Richter install cameras without telling anyone.

1061
01:54:22,721 --> 01:54:25,423
To keep an eye on him for his safety.

1062
01:54:27,186 --> 01:54:28,861
Maybe it records.

1063
01:54:39,427 --> 01:54:43,572
<i>- I read the journals, Patrick.
- The scientist kept journals. So?</i>

1064
01:54:44,173 --> 01:54:46,939
<i>- You figure prominently in them.
- Really?</i>

1065
01:54:47,460 --> 01:54:51,741
<i>The Devoli wasn't just a physicist.
He was also a Catholic priest.</i>

1066
01:54:52,239 --> 01:54:58,400
As such, he was deeply conflicted about the implications
of his work and in need of spiritual guidance.

1067
01:54:59,034 --> 01:55:00,198
Like Galileo.

1068
01:55:01,500 --> 01:55:04,711
About a month ago, he requested an audience with the Pope.

1069
01:55:04,713 --> 01:55:06,113
But you know that,

1070
01:55:06,705 --> 01:55:09,586
cause you granted the audience and
you were also present during it.

1071
01:55:09,688 --> 01:55:12,866
The 'God Particle'. To actually claim an act of creation.

1072
01:55:12,867 --> 01:55:17,154
- The blasphemy. The arrogance.
- The Holy Father didn't see it like that.

1073
01:55:17,459 --> 01:55:19,359
He urged him to go public.

1074
01:55:19,564 --> 01:55:25,475
His Holiness thought that the discovery could actually
scientifically prove the existence of a divine power.

1075
01:55:25,611 --> 01:55:28,614
And begin to bridge the gap between science and religion.

1076
01:55:28,718 --> 01:55:31,120
His work was not religious.
It was sacrilegious.

1077
01:55:31,122 --> 01:55:32,034
But you...

1078
01:55:32,724 --> 01:55:36,664
You saw the pope's position as a softening of church law.

1079
01:55:36,669 --> 01:55:40,484
As an old man's weakness. Your father's weakness.

1080
01:55:40,819 --> 01:55:44,420
- You murdered the Vicar of Christ.
- He raised me to protect this Church,

1081
01:55:44,458 --> 01:55:45,923
even from within.

1082
01:55:47,600 --> 01:55:52,250
Then you conjured up an old enemy from the past.
The Illuminati.

1083
01:55:52,485 --> 01:55:57,550
You found the ancient brands in the papal vaults
and put them to use to spread fear!

1084
01:55:57,550 --> 01:55:59,792
The Cardinals are men of belief.

1085
01:56:00,200 --> 01:56:03,715
Right now, their belief in evil is uniting them.

1086
01:56:03,716 --> 01:56:06,815
The entire Catholic world will be united by this attack.

1087
01:56:06,820 --> 01:56:08,402
There is no attack.

1088
01:56:09,690 --> 01:56:14,443
You're trying to convince the Cardinals they're in a war,
so they will choose a warrior to lead them.

1089
01:56:14,442 --> 01:56:15,776
We are at war.

1090
01:56:15,878 --> 01:56:17,915
We're weak when we should be strong.

1091
01:56:17,919 --> 01:56:21,614
If science is allowed to claim the power of creation,

1092
01:56:21,828 --> 01:56:23,586
what is left for God?

1093
01:56:23,821 --> 01:56:25,545
It didn't work, Patrick.

1094
01:56:26,533 --> 01:56:29,219
- It isn't finished.
- Oh yes, it's finished.

1095
01:56:31,191 --> 01:56:32,882
It's finished.

1096
01:56:33,740 --> 01:56:36,845
I've shown the journals to Father Simeon.

1097
01:56:36,851 --> 01:56:38,931
The moment the doors to the Conclave open,

1098
01:56:38,937 --> 01:56:41,092
he will tell the Cardinals what you've done.

1099
01:56:42,181 --> 01:56:44,391
I was planning on doing this alone.

1100
01:56:47,466 --> 01:56:48,850
Put it down.

1101
01:56:51,565 --> 01:56:53,892
But, perhaps, it's better that you're here.

1102
01:56:53,939 --> 01:56:55,320
Put it down.

1103
01:56:57,219 --> 01:56:58,956
Put it away.

1104
01:57:09,424 --> 01:57:13,620
Help. He's the one.
He's got a gun.

1105
01:57:17,264 --> 01:57:19,396
- Illuminatus!
- You bastard.

1106
01:57:19,553 --> 01:57:20,415
Illuminatus!

1107
01:57:20,416 --> 01:57:21,967
You bastard!

1108
01:57:25,946 --> 01:57:27,153
Padre.

1109
01:57:36,755 --> 01:57:40,223
<i>And get the helicopter for the older cardinals, right?</i>

1110
01:58:29,171 --> 01:58:32,214
I've been summoned by the College of Cardinals.

1111
01:59:42,037 --> 01:59:43,556
Gently.

1112
01:59:43,564 --> 01:59:45,238
But within our walls.

1113
01:59:56,960 --> 01:59:59,823
He's on your side.

1114
02:00:45,853 --> 02:00:50,061
Father, into thy hands I commend my spirit.

1115
02:01:37,960 --> 02:01:42,368
Church sources now confirm that Carmelengo,
Father Patrick McKenna,

1116
02:01:42,369 --> 02:01:48,112
has died of internal injuries sustained in his heroic fall...

1117
02:01:47,920 --> 02:01:54,000
The Catholic church thanks Camerlengo for his selfless act
and demands his immediate canonization.

1118
02:01:54,340 --> 02:01:59,400
The Vatican has also confirmed the deaths of three Cardinals
and the fire in the Santa Maria della Vittoria.

1119
02:01:59,446 --> 02:02:03,821
As we await the appearance of the new
Holy Father Cardinal Baggia of Italy,

1120
02:02:03,822 --> 02:02:09,665
one of the four original Preferiti, who, despite terrorist
attempts at disruption seems to have been selected

1121
02:02:09,666 --> 02:02:13,822
in one of the swiftest and smoothest conclaves
in modern church history.

1122
02:02:20,516 --> 02:02:22,669
Professor Langdon? Please.

1123
02:02:39,010 --> 02:02:41,859
A token of thanks from His Holiness

1124
02:02:42,361 --> 02:02:44,799
and from his new Camerlengo.

1125
02:02:46,573 --> 02:02:48,828
We are grateful you saved his life.

1126
02:02:49,455 --> 02:02:54,870
And it's our understanding that you require this text
to complete your scholary work.

1127
02:02:56,603 --> 02:02:59,798
We ask only that in your last grand testament

1128
02:03:00,067 --> 02:03:03,861
you ensure it finds its way home.

1129
02:03:06,674 --> 02:03:07,623
Of course.

1130
02:03:08,141 --> 02:03:09,811
And when you write of us,

1131
02:03:10,534 --> 02:03:12,583
and you will write of us,

1132
02:03:13,032 --> 02:03:14,776
may I ask one thing?

1133
02:03:15,473 --> 02:03:16,996
Do so gently.

1134
02:03:19,348 --> 02:03:20,485
I'll try.

1135
02:03:21,081 --> 02:03:22,485
Religion is flawed,

1136
02:03:23,458 --> 02:03:26,063
but only because man is flawed.

1137
02:03:26,064 --> 02:03:28,681
All men, including this one.

1138
02:03:43,525 --> 02:03:45,177
He chose the name Luke.

1139
02:03:48,087 --> 02:03:50,862
There's been many Marks and Johns.

1140
02:03:52,367 --> 02:03:53,843
Never a Luke.

1141
02:03:54,608 --> 02:03:56,337
It said he was a doctor.

1142
02:03:57,081 --> 02:04:00,301
It's quite a message.
Science and faith, all in one.

1143
02:04:01,106 --> 02:04:03,273
The world is in need of both.

1144
02:04:05,283 --> 02:04:07,126
You'll counsel him wisely.

1145
02:04:07,981 --> 02:04:10,774
I'm an old man.
I'll counsel him briefly.

1146
02:04:16,800 --> 02:04:18,466
Mr. Langdon.

1147
02:04:23,489 --> 02:04:28,210
Thanks be to God for sending someone to protect this church.

1148
02:04:32,241 --> 02:04:34,883
I don't believe He sent me, Father.

1149
02:04:35,084 --> 02:04:36,704
Oh, my son.

1150
02:04:37,266 --> 02:04:39,485
Of course He did.

